room_title: Escape room "The Submarine" by Last Minute Escape in New York
room_description: In the Pacific Theater during WWII, you are the crew of submariners on the water front lines. The captain and his officers have been taken prisoner, so the outcome of the operation is in your hands! If you manage to load the torpedo, contact Naval Command and launch it at the enemy battlecruiser in time you may make the waters safe again and bring the USA that much closer to victory!
